resources.string: Hello Buddies,Stack Overflow helps people find the answers they need, when they need them. We\'re best known for our public QA platform that over 100 million people visit every month to ask questions, learn, and share technical knowledge. Our products and tools empower people to find what they need to develop technology at work or at home. These products include, Stack Overflow for Teams, Stack Overflow Advertising, Collectives™ on Stack Overflow, and Stack Overflow Talent.
